Key to deep-water species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Day" authorityYear="1977" box="[513,686,969,996]" class="Polychaeta" family="Orbiniidae" genus="Leitoscoloplos" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
